it means the saved people

00:45:15.680 --> 00:45:17.680
brothers and sisters in Christ

00:45:17.680 --> 00:45:20.680
those who have been saved by the blood of Christ

00:45:20.680 --> 00:45:23.680
he says now concerning spiritual gifts brethren

00:45:23.680 --> 00:45:25.680
so he's writing to saved people

00:45:25.680 --> 00:45:28.680
and he's writing to them about spiritual gifts

00:45:28.680 --> 00:45:31.680
and he says I would not have you ignorant

00:45:31.680 --> 00:45:32.680
I want you to understand this

00:45:32.680 --> 00:45:34.680
I want you to be informed of this

00:45:34.680 --> 00:45:37.680
I want you to have a proper understanding

00:45:37.680 --> 00:45:40.680
by the way aren't you thankful that God has given us his word?

00:45:40.680 --> 00:45:42.680
and he's instructed us

00:45:42.680 --> 00:45:44.680
I mean he's given it to us

00:45:44.680 --> 00:45:45.680
he says this in verse 2

00:45:45.680 --> 00:45:47.680
ye know that ye were Gentiles

00:45:47.680 --> 00:45:48.680
that we were lost

00:45:48.680 --> 00:45:50.680
carried away into these dumb idols

00:45:50.680 --> 00:45:51.680
even as you were led

00:45:51.680 --> 00:45:54.680
wherefore I give you to understand

00:45:54.680 --> 00:45:56.680
that no man speaking by the spirit of God

00:45:56.680 --> 00:45:57.680
calleth Jesus a curse

00:45:57.680 --> 00:46:00.680
and that no man can say that Jesus is the Lord

00:46:00.680 --> 00:46:02.680
but by the Holy Ghost

00:46:02.680 --> 00:46:05.680
now there are notice in verse 4

00:46:05.680 --> 00:46:07.680
diversities of gifts

00:46:07.680 --> 00:46:09.680
but the same spirit

00:46:09.680 --> 00:46:11.680
so we don't all have the same gift

00:46:11.680 --> 00:46:13.680
the same spiritual gift

00:46:13.680 --> 00:46:15.680
he says there's diversity of gifts

00:46:15.680 --> 00:46:16.680
but the same spirit

00:46:16.680 --> 00:46:17.680
notice in verse 5

00:46:17.680 --> 00:46:20.680
and there are differences of administration

00:46:20.680 --> 00:46:21.680
but the same Lord

00:46:21.680 --> 00:46:23.680
and there are diversities of operations

00:46:23.680 --> 00:46:25.680
but it is the same God

00:46:25.680 --> 00:46:28.680
which worketh all in all

00:46:28.680 --> 00:46:29.680
but the manifestation of the spirit

00:46:29.680 --> 00:46:31.680
is given to every man

00:46:31.680 --> 00:46:32.680
to profit with all

00:46:32.680 --> 00:46:34.680
so we really see that there's two purposes

00:46:34.680 --> 00:46:35.680
of spiritual gifts

00:46:35.680 --> 00:46:37.680
one in primary

00:46:37.680 --> 00:46:40.680
is to bring honor and glory to God

00:46:40.680 --> 00:46:42.680
but number 2 is to profit with all

00:46:42.680 --> 00:46:43.680
according to verse number 7

00:46:43.680 --> 00:46:45.680
of 1st Corinthians chapter 12

00:46:45.680 --> 00:46:46.680
what do we mean to profit with all

00:46:46.680 --> 00:46:47.680
well it's a benefit

00:46:47.680 --> 00:46:49.680
to the local assembly

00:46:49.680 --> 00:46:51.680
when you use your spiritual gift

00:46:51.680 --> 00:46:53.680
and when I use my spiritual gift

00:46:53.680 --> 00:46:55.680
then it profits the body

00:46:55.680 --> 00:46:56.680
that's how it works

00:46:56.680 --> 00:46:58.680
that's how God designed it

00:46:58.680 --> 00:47:00.680
we find that he says in verse number 8

00:47:00.680 --> 00:47:02.680
for to one is given by the spirit

00:47:02.680 --> 00:47:03.680
now by who?

00:47:03.680 --> 00:47:04.680
by the spirit

00:47:04.680 --> 00:47:05.680
who's the spirit?

00:47:05.680 --> 00:47:07.680
well that's the third person of the Godhead

00:47:07.680 --> 00:47:08.680
the Holy Spirit of God

00:47:08.680 --> 00:47:09.680
the Bible says

00:47:09.680 --> 00:47:10.680
for to one is given by the spirit

00:47:10.680 --> 00:47:11.680
the word of wisdom

00:47:11.680 --> 00:47:12.680
to another the word of knowledge

00:47:12.680 --> 00:47:14.680
by the same spirit

00:47:14.680 --> 00:47:15.680
to another faith

00:47:15.680 --> 00:47:16.680
by the same spirit

00:47:16.680 --> 00:47:17.680
to another the gifts of healing

00:47:17.680 --> 00:47:18.680
of the same spirit

00:47:18.680 --> 00:47:19.680
to another the working of miracles

00:47:19.680 --> 00:47:20.680
to another prophecy

00:47:20.680 --> 00:47:22.680
to another discerning of spirits

00:47:22.680 --> 00:47:23.680
to another diverse kinds of tongues

00:47:23.680 --> 00:47:25.680
to another the interpretation of tongues

00:47:25.680 --> 00:47:27.680
but all these worketh

00:47:27.680 --> 00:47:29.680
that one and the self

00:47:29.680 --> 00:47:30.680
same spirit

00:47:30.680 --> 00:47:31.680
notice this

00:47:31.680 --> 00:47:33.680
dividing to every man

00:47:33.680 --> 00:47:34.680
severally

00:47:34.680 --> 00:47:35.680
notice these words

00:47:35.680 --> 00:47:37.680
as he will

00:47:37.680 --> 00:47:39.680
it's God's will

00:47:39.680 --> 00:47:41.680
and God gives the gifts

00:47:41.680 --> 00:47:42.680
I don't have time this morning

00:47:42.680 --> 00:47:43.680
to develop all of this

00:47:43.680 --> 00:47:44.680
from first Corinthians 12

00:47:44.680 --> 00:47:45.680
with regard to the

00:47:45.680 --> 00:47:47.680
temporary sign gifts

00:47:47.680 --> 00:47:48.680
that God gave

00:47:48.680 --> 00:47:49.680
and how God was

00:47:49.680 --> 00:47:51.680
authenticating his word

00:47:51.680 --> 00:47:52.680
through some of those

00:47:52.680 --> 00:47:53.680
temporary sign gifts

00:47:53.680 --> 00:47:55.680
we find that first Corinthians

00:47:55.680 --> 00:47:56.680
is the first

00:47:56.680 --> 00:47:57.680
the oldest of the books

00:47:57.680 --> 00:47:58.680
that is written

00:47:58.680 --> 00:48:00.680
with regard to spiritual gifts

00:48:00.680 --> 00:48:01.680
you get to the book of Romans

00:48:01.680 --> 00:48:02.680
you get to the book of Ephesians

00:48:02.680 --> 00:48:04.680
and there are several of these

00:48:04.680 --> 00:48:05.680
that are not even mentioned

00:48:05.680 --> 00:48:06.680
at that point

00:48:06.680 --> 00:48:07.680
with regard to those

00:48:07.680 --> 00:48:09.680
temporary sign gifts

00:48:09.680 --> 00:48:11.680
but we find the importance

00:48:11.680 --> 00:48:12.680
of this as dividing to every man

00:48:12.680 --> 00:48:13.680
severally as he will

00:48:13.680 --> 00:48:15.680
now notice in verse 12

00:48:15.680 --> 00:48:17.680
for as the body is one

00:48:17.680 --> 00:48:19.680
and hath many members

00:48:19.680 --> 00:48:21.680
and all the members of that

00:48:21.680 --> 00:48:22.680
one body

00:48:22.680 --> 00:48:23.680
being many

00:48:23.680 --> 00:48:24.680
are one body

00:48:24.680 --> 00:48:26.680
so also is Christ

00:48:26.680 --> 00:48:27.680
so notice what he's saying

00:48:27.680 --> 00:48:29.680
as he's giving this truth

00:48:29.680 --> 00:48:30.680
with regard to the

00:48:30.680 --> 00:48:32.680
spiritual gifts

00:48:32.680 --> 00:48:34.680
he says there's diversity

00:48:34.680 --> 00:48:35.680
but then he says

00:48:35.680 --> 00:48:37.680
that there's one body

00:48:37.680 --> 00:48:38.680
and though

00:48:38.680 --> 00:48:39.680
and he uses the illustration

00:48:39.680 --> 00:48:41.680
of our human body

00:48:41.680 --> 00:48:42.680
and we know

00:48:42.680 --> 00:48:43.680
listen I'm happy

00:48:43.680 --> 00:48:44.680
that I don't have

00:48:44.680 --> 00:48:45.680
two left hands

00:48:45.680 --> 00:48:46.680
how many of you are happy

00:48:46.680 --> 00:48:47.680
you don't have two left hands

00:48:47.680 --> 00:48:48.680
amen

00:48:48.680 --> 00:48:49.680
my left hand sometimes

00:48:49.680 --> 00:48:50.680
I think doesn't listen

00:48:50.680 --> 00:48:51.680
to my brain right

00:48:51.680 --> 00:48:52.680
and I say what is going on

00:48:52.680 --> 00:48:53.680
it's not doing what

00:48:53.680 --> 00:48:54.680
I want it to do

00:48:54.680 --> 00:48:55.680
and God has given us

00:48:55.680 --> 00:48:56.680
listen I'm thankful

00:48:56.680 --> 00:48:58.680
to have eyes and ears

00:48:58.680 --> 00:48:59.680
I'm thankful

00:48:59.680 --> 00:49:00.680
that I have these

00:49:00.680 --> 00:49:01.680
listen if the eye says

00:49:01.680 --> 00:49:02.680
I'm not going to do

00:49:02.680 --> 00:49:03.680
because I'm not

00:49:03.680 --> 00:49:04.680
if the hand says

00:49:04.680 --> 00:49:05.680
I'm not going to

00:49:05.680 --> 00:49:06.680
that's what he goes through

00:49:06.680 --> 00:49:08.680
in chapter 12

00:49:08.680 --> 00:49:09.680
but God has given us

00:49:09.680 --> 00:49:10.680
all of these things

00:49:10.680 --> 00:49:11.680
as he's made our body

00:49:11.680 --> 00:49:12.680
by the way

00:49:12.680 --> 00:49:15.680
he formed us perfectly

00:49:15.680 --> 00:49:18.680
he formed us perfectly

00:49:18.680 --> 00:49:19.680
and then he says

00:49:19.680 --> 00:49:20.680
I'm going to use that analogy

00:49:20.680 --> 00:49:22.680
that example of the body

00:49:22.680 --> 00:49:23.680
and you understand

00:49:23.680 --> 00:49:25.680
how your body functions

00:49:25.680 --> 00:49:26.680
as one body

00:49:26.680 --> 00:49:28.680
though we have various members

00:49:28.680 --> 00:49:29.680
so the body of Christ

00:49:29.680 --> 00:49:30.680
is to function

00:49:30.680 --> 00:49:32.680
in the same way

00:49:32.680 --> 00:49:33.680
and so the body of Christ

00:49:33.680 --> 00:49:34.680
is made up of

00:49:34.680 --> 00:49:37.680
various individuals

00:49:37.680 --> 00:49:38.680
but we're one body

00:49:38.680 --> 00:49:40.680
those various individuals

00:49:40.680 --> 00:49:42.680
have varying spiritual gifts

00:49:42.680 --> 00:49:44.680
but we're one body

00:49:44.680 --> 00:49:45.680
and as we understand

00:49:45.680 --> 00:49:47.680
that it's the Holy Spirit of God

00:49:47.680 --> 00:49:48.680
who has gifted us

00:49:48.680 --> 00:49:50.680
who has brought us together

00:49:50.680 --> 00:49:51.680
as one body

00:49:51.680 --> 00:49:52.680
to fulfill his mission

00:49:52.680 --> 00:49:54.680
to fulfill the ministry

00:49:54.680 --> 00:49:55.680
then I say

00:49:55.680 --> 00:49:57.680
I want to be profitable

00:49:57.680 --> 00:49:59.680
for the ministry

00:49:59.680 --> 00:50:03.800
You ever heard the phrase that the team or the group

00:50:03.800 --> 00:50:06.480
is only as good as its weakest link?

00:50:06.480 --> 00:50:08.960
You heard people use that phraseology?

00:50:08.960 --> 00:50:10.280
Listen, I don't wanna be the one

00:50:10.280 --> 00:50:12.480
that's unprofitable for the ministry.

00:50:12.480 --> 00:50:15.480
I wanna be the one that's profitable for the ministry.

00:50:15.480 --> 00:50:17.520
And if we recognize this morning,

00:50:17.520 --> 00:50:21.000
as we think about this truth where Paul is writing of Mark

00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:24.400
and he says to Timothy, listen, bring Mark,

00:50:24.400 --> 00:50:27.160
take Mark and bring him with thee, why?

00:50:27.160 --> 00:50:31.820
For he is profitable to me for the ministry.

00:50:31.820 --> 00:50:33.740
We understand what the ministry is,

00:50:33.740 --> 00:50:37.060
but then we must discover our place in the ministry.

00:50:37.060 --> 00:50:38.720
What does God have for me?

00:50:38.720 --> 00:50:42.240
If we recognize this morning that God has equipped you

00:50:42.240 --> 00:50:44.220
personally, individually,

00:50:44.220 --> 00:50:48.340
he has given to you a spiritual gift.

00:50:48.340 --> 00:50:50.580
And with giving you that spiritual gift,

00:50:50.580 --> 00:50:55.580
he has the expectation that you would be a good steward

00:50:56.220 --> 00:50:58.260
of what he has given to you

00:50:58.260 --> 00:51:00.740
and that you would use your spiritual gift

00:51:00.740 --> 00:51:05.020
to bring honor and glory to him and to profit the body.

00:51:06.740 --> 00:51:09.380
And by the way, it's okay for God

00:51:09.380 --> 00:51:10.940
to have that expectation of us

00:51:10.940 --> 00:51:13.460
because he's the one that gave us the gift.

00:51:14.600 --> 00:51:15.520
Amen?

00:51:15.520 --> 00:51:18.860
He gave it to us and then he expects

00:51:18.860 --> 00:51:22.960
that we would use it for his honor and for his glory.

00:51:22.960 --> 00:51:25.500
You ever hear about Moses?

00:51:26.320 --> 00:51:28.020
Of course, Moses, a household name.

00:51:28.900 --> 00:51:33.900
Bezalel, Holyab, not as well known.

00:51:35.660 --> 00:51:37.480
But you know who those men are?

00:51:37.480 --> 00:51:39.620
Those are the men that God equipped

00:51:39.620 --> 00:51:42.860
to do the work for the tabernacle.

00:51:42.860 --> 00:51:45.840
Moses was the one that was given the blueprints,

00:51:45.840 --> 00:51:47.580
if you will.

00:51:47.580 --> 00:51:51.100
But God says to Moses, I've equipped these men,

00:51:51.100 --> 00:51:54.540
not only to do, but then also to teach others.

00:51:54.540 --> 00:51:56.860
And you know what God expected of Bezalel?

00:51:56.860 --> 00:51:59.060
He expected that he would do the work

00:51:59.060 --> 00:52:00.760
that he equipped him to do.

00:52:01.860 --> 00:52:04.300
God's equipped us this morning.

00:52:04.300 --> 00:52:05.420
And I just wonder today,

00:52:05.420 --> 00:52:08.500
as I look at this passage of scripture

00:52:08.500 --> 00:52:12.820
in 2 Timothy 4, and I read those words

00:52:12.820 --> 00:52:17.820
that he is profitable to me for the ministry.

00:52:18.780 --> 00:52:20.600
Of course, this morning is not the first time

00:52:20.600 --> 00:52:22.320
I ever read these words.

00:52:23.080 --> 00:52:26.280
I do remember, not the day or the time,

00:52:26.280 --> 00:52:29.180
but I remember the first time I ever read these words.

00:52:30.280 --> 00:52:32.200
And I remember reading these words

00:52:33.400 --> 00:52:35.220
and asking myself this question.

00:52:36.440 --> 00:52:38.920
Would it be said of me that I'm profitable

00:52:38.920 --> 00:52:39.860
for the ministry?

00:52:41.040 --> 00:52:42.360
I've been saved for 27 years.

00:52:42.360 --> 00:52:44.580
It was probably 25, 26 years ago

00:52:44.580 --> 00:52:46.720
that I read those words for the first time.

00:52:47.880 --> 00:52:50.040
And God used those words to grip my heart.

00:52:51.040 --> 00:52:54.280
And I had to answer that question honestly and humbly.

00:52:54.280 --> 00:52:56.280
Would I be profitable for the ministry?

00:52:56.280 --> 00:53:01.280
If my pastor was writing,

00:53:01.780 --> 00:53:03.800
would he say, bring him because he's profitable

00:53:03.800 --> 00:53:05.120
to me for the ministry?

00:53:06.600 --> 00:53:09.640
And I desire that for myself,

00:53:09.640 --> 00:53:11.760
and I hope that you would desire for yourself

00:53:11.760 --> 00:53:13.920
this morning as well,

00:53:13.920 --> 00:53:16.580
that God would say of each of us

00:53:16.580 --> 00:53:20.320
that we are profitable for the ministry,

00:53:20.320 --> 00:53:22.940
that we're fulfilling the work

00:53:22.940 --> 00:53:25.820
that God has equipped us to do,

00:53:25.820 --> 00:53:27.340
that we're not negligent,

00:53:27.340 --> 00:53:30.420
that we're not MIA, right?

00:53:30.420 --> 00:53:31.260
No, no, no.

00:53:31.260 --> 00:53:33.060
We're doing what God has called us to do.

00:53:33.060 --> 00:53:34.720
And you say, but it's only, no, no, no.

00:53:34.720 --> 00:53:36.260
It's not, but it's only.

00:53:36.260 --> 00:53:37.780
If God equipped you for it,

00:53:37.780 --> 00:53:39.700
it's the most important thing.

00:53:39.700 --> 00:53:43.260
And by the way, the only thing that you're accountable for

00:53:43.260 --> 00:53:45.640
is to do what God equipped you to do.

00:53:45.640 --> 00:53:46.520
So we come to the place and say,

00:53:46.520 --> 00:53:48.600
God, I understand the ministry.

00:53:48.600 --> 00:53:50.040
We've defined it.

00:53:50.040 --> 00:53:51.960
God, I wanna discover my place in the ministry.

00:53:51.960 --> 00:53:54.960
God, I want you to use me for your honor and for your glory.

00:53:54.960 --> 00:53:56.140
Thank you for enabling me.

00:53:56.140 --> 00:53:57.240
Thank you for equipping me.

00:53:57.240 --> 00:54:00.440
Now use me in your work.

00:54:00.440 --> 00:54:02.500
What a joy it is to be used of God.

00:54:02.500 --> 00:54:03.340
Let's pray.

00:54:03.340 --> 00:54:04.400
Father, we love you.

00:54:04.400 --> 00:54:06.340
How we thank you for loving us.

00:54:07.720 --> 00:54:10.140
Thank you for using us.

00:54:10.140 --> 00:54:11.660
We thank you for saving us,

00:54:11.660 --> 00:54:14.880
and we understand that you saved us to service.

00:54:14.960 --> 00:54:16.780
And Lord, I pray that as we,

00:54:18.840 --> 00:54:21.800
this morning would rejoice in our salvation,

00:54:21.800 --> 00:54:23.600
that we'd also rejoice in the fact

00:54:23.600 --> 00:54:25.280
that we are your workmanship,

00:54:26.240 --> 00:54:27.680
that you saved us to serve.

00:54:27.680 --> 00:54:30.380
And Lord, I pray you help us to discover

00:54:30.380 --> 00:54:31.600
our place in the ministry.

00:54:31.600 --> 00:54:34.800
I pray that we'd evaluate our hearts and our own lives

00:54:34.800 --> 00:54:36.480
here in this moment of invitation

00:54:37.720 --> 00:54:40.080
to contemplate that question

00:54:40.080 --> 00:54:43.600
of whether or not it would be said of us as individuals

00:54:43.600 --> 00:54:46.440
that we're profitable for the ministry.

00:54:47.400 --> 00:54:50.360
I pray the Holy Spirit of God would have his will and way.

00:54:51.440 --> 00:54:55.180
Decisions would be made that would please you, Lord.

00:54:55.180 --> 00:54:56.760
We'll thank you for the work that you'll do.

00:54:56.760 --> 00:54:58.120
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:54:58.120 --> 00:54:59.320
We just stand with you.

